.page-container
  / bloc-0
  #bloc-0.bloc.bloc-fill-screen.lake-hero-bloc.bg-map.bgc-caribbean-green.d-bloc
    = render 'application/header'

    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-12
    .container.fill-bloc-bottom-edge
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          = image_tag "youinno.png", class: 'img-responsive', width: 600
  / bloc-0 END
  / bloc-1
  #bloc-1.bloc.tc-white.bgc-onyx
    .container.bloc-lg
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          %h2.mg-md
            혁신의 편에 서기 위한 조건을 듣고,
            %br>/
            정책 전문가의 도움을 받아
            %br>/
            대선 정책으로 제안합니다.
            %br/
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-sq.btn-wire.wire-btn-safety-orange-blaze-orange{:href => "index.html"} 프로젝트 소개
        .col-sm-6
          %p
            소개를 적습니다.
            %br
            OFA is committed to mobilizing and training
            %br
            the next generation of progressive organizers and leaders,
            %br
            because real, lasting change doesn&rsquo;t just happen on its own—
            %br
            it requires a program, it requires organizing,
            %br
            and it requires people like you.
            %br

            %br
            With grassroots chapters in neighborhoods across the country,
            %br
            OFA volunteers are building this movement from the ground up,
            %br
            person to person, community by community—
            %br
            because democracy isn&rsquo;t a spectator sport.&nbsp;
            %br


