            %br

          = link_to '인사이트 보고 의견 남기기', insights_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-wire btn-sq wire-btn-safety-orange-blaze-orange'
        .col-sm-6
          %p

            %br

            %br

            %br
            %u 사회적기업 FGI
            &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;
            %br

            %br
            OFA is committed to mobilizing and training
            %br
            the next generation of progressive organizers and leaders,
